    <briefdescription>
<para>OSUSat/SCRT Messaging Standard Packet Library. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides structures and functions to serialize and deserialize packets. This library is designed to be portable and avoid dynamic memory allocation. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
